{"tid":1143009,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★派4000蚊一鑊粥惹怒氣　陳茂波落區遲到遇示威","createTime":"2019-05-07T12:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T04:41:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8db306bf54351003cb44ff7269efac8b3cc31dd5","tid":1143009,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:32:55.000Z","msg":"政府去年公布派發4000港元的關愛共享計劃，但申請連場混亂，不時被斥擾民低效。財政司司長陳茂波今午(7日)到訪葵青區議會，約40人於葵青區議會所在的葵興政府合署外進行請願活動，請願人士批評計劃籌備多時但安排混亂，直言未知何時才能獲派發4000港元，有人更要求政府盡快派發款項，甚至派多3000港元以平息市民對連番混亂的怒氣，又要求政府簡化派錢程序。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有請願人士不滿政府動用公帑發展「明日大嶼」填海計劃，批評陳茂波胡亂用錢，猶如倒錢落海，亦有請願人士要求增設長者牙科門診、實報實銷牙科津貼、增加醫療券及取消累積上限。<br />\n<br />\n此外，陳茂波較原定時間稍遲到場，遭在場等候的長者斥罵遲到，直言已等候多時，而陳在接收所有請願信後，才前往區議會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190507/bkn-20190507175731318-0507_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190507%2Fbkn-20190507175731318-0507_00822_001.html&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8S3PcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=76a54bb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190507/bkn-20190507175731318-0507_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0c8618baf104f694e9824f8a1b00dff240e6888c","tid":1143009,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e8d9246231f2567a1a40ed4074883107fea108","tid":1143009,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190507/photo/bkn-20190507175731318-0507_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190507181342\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190507%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190507175731318-0507_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20190507181342&h=01102